  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFFim Frontload for CEPI</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFFIm issues Vaccine Bonds in the capital markets and repay these bonds with long-term donor pledges. IFFIm will frontload pledges made by the Norwegian Government to CEPI in 2021-2025, for the use in the years 2019-2021. CEPI is a partnership of public, private and humanitarian org. The Coalition will fund/stimulate development of vaccines against selected diseases with potential for becoming major epidemics.</narrative>
  </description>
